data.description: New Listing located in East New York, Brooklyn. Commercial unit and 2 residential units. This mixed-use property features commercial space currently being used as a nail salon, 1 one bedroom apartment and a two bedroom on the 2nd floor, 1 retail unit on the ground floor and a full basement. Steps away from the B15, B83 Bus and walking distance to the 2,3 trains. Call today to schedule an appointment. Motivated seller.
